the life and death of john gotti , originally titled gotti : in the shadow of my father , is an upcoming american biographical crime drama film directed by kevin connolly and written by lem dobbs and leo rossi .   the film is about the life of new york city mobster john gotti and his son .   the film stars john travolta , kelly preston , stacy keach , pruitt taylor vince , spencer lofranco and victor gojcaj .   principal photography on the film began on july 25 , 2016 , in cincinnati , ohio and concluded on february 21 , 2017 in brooklyn , new york .